'''馬修·波特歷'''（{{lang-en|Matthew Broderick}}，{{bd|1962年|3月21日|||catIdx=Broderick}}），[[美國電影|美國電影]]及[[舞台|舞台]]演員，作品多是[[喜劇片|喜劇片]]。成名作為[[百老匯|百老匯]][[舞臺劇|舞臺劇]]《[[Torch_Song_Trilogy|Torch Song Trilogy]]》，代表作有《[[咪走堂|咪走堂]]》等。

==早期生活==
馬修·柏德瑞克出生在美國紐約市<ref name=":0" />。馬修·柏德瑞克的母親是[[猶太人|猶太人]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://jewishjournal.com/culture/arts/12403/|title=Bialystock and Bloom Tell the Truth|accessdate=May 16, 2018|date=December 15, 2005|last=Tugend|first=Tom|work=Jewish Journal|quote=Matthew Broderick: "I suppose so. I mean, yeah. My mom was Jewish, so some would call me Jewish."|archive-date=2018-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180217203106/http://jewishjournal.com/culture/arts/12403/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://abcnews.go.com/GMA/story?id=1429337|title=Excerpt: 'Stars of David : Prominent Jews Talk About Being Jewish' by Abigail Pogrebin|work=ABC News|date=December 26, 2005|accessdate=May 16, 2018|quote=actor Matthew Broderick -- whose mother was Jewish|archive-date=2018-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180516175125/https://abcnews.go.com/GMA/story?id=1429337|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Austin|last=O'Connor|url=https://www.aarp.org/entertainment/television/info-2017/matthew-broderick-interview-fd.html|title=Matthew Broderick's Christmas Presence|work=AARP|date=December 14, 2017|accessdate=May 16, 2018|archive-date=2018-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180516174648/https://www.aarp.org/entertainment/television/info-2017/matthew-broderick-interview-fd.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Barbara|last=Hoffman|url=https://nypost.com/2018/04/19/matthew-broderick-cynthia-nixon-will-have-to-work-for-my-vote/|title=Matthew Broderick: Cynthia Nixon will have to work for my vote|work=New York Post|date=April 19, 2018|accessdate=May 16, 2018|archive-date=2018-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180516175306/https://nypost.com/2018/04/19/matthew-broderick-cynthia-nixon-will-have-to-work-for-my-vote/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但她沒有信奉[[猶太教|猶太教]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.stljewishlight.com/features/article_27d2ff80-db75-11e7-81ca-3346fc71e048.html|title=‘Tis the season for the Goldbergs to face the ‘December Dilemma’|accessdate=May 16, 2018|date=December 7, 2017|last=Bloom|first=Nate|work=St. Louis Jewish Light|quote=Matthew Broderick’s mother was Jewish and while not religious.|archive-date=2018-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180102142241/http://www.stljewishlight.com/features/article_27d2ff80-db75-11e7-81ca-3346fc71e048.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。馬修·柏德瑞克的父親有愛爾蘭血統和英格蘭血統<ref name=":0">{{cite news | title = Matthew Broderick - Biography | url = http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0000111/bio | work = IMDb | accessdate = 2017-11-24 | archive-date = 2020-11-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201109040727/http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0000111/bio | dead-url = no }}</ref>。母親Patricia Broderick是劇作家，父親James Broderick是演員<ref name=":0" />。

